Definition: any of various perennial South American plants of the genus Loasa having stinging hairs and showy white or yellow or reddish-orange flowers
Synonyms: herb, genus_Loasa, m, any, of, various, perennial, South, American, plants, the, genus, Loasa, having, stinging, hairs, and, showy, white, or, yellow, reddish-orange, flowers
Category: noun.plant
